Template: multiflexi-zabbix/zabbix_server
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Zabbix server address:
 Please enter the address (hostname or IP) of your Zabbix server.

Template: multiflexi-zabbix/zabbix_host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Zabbix host name:
 Please enter the name of this host as it is registered in Zabbix.

Template: multiflexi-zabbix/use_zabbix_sender
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Use zabbix_sender binary?
 If set to true, the package will use the external zabbix_sender command
 instead of the internal PHP implementation.
